### Pokémon API - Testing Endpoints
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@pokemonId = 6901ad5a893e55a4b5d0ed79

### 1. Crear un Pokémon - Pikachu
POST {{baseUrl}}/pokemon
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pikachu",
  "type": "Electric",
  "hp": 35,
  "attack": 55,
  "defense": 40,
  "spAtk": 50,
  "spDef": 50,
  "speed": 90
}

